OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777114970
OL,3,CVeteran plans to become first triple
OL,4,Camputee to complete London Marathon
OL,6,FThe 49-year-old, from St Helens in
OL,7,FMerseyside, will also be walking the
OL,8,Froute on Sunday in honour of the seven
OL,9,Fmembers of his regiment, his friends,
OL,10,Fwhom he lost, saying: "I'm still here
OL,11,Fdespite my injury, so I've got to make
OL,12,Fthe most of life."
OL,14,FMr Reid told the Press Association he
OL,15,Fis taking on the challenge "to show
OL,16,Fother people with a disability or
OL,17,Finjury what can be achieved with the
OL,18,Fright mindset and with the right
OL,19,Fsupport network around them".
OL,26,@rD@WOUtD@RO]wD@\OU{D@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
