FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777114970
OL,3,CVeteran plans to become first triple
OL,4,Camputee to complete London Marathon
OL,6,FHe continued: "New Year's Day I
OL,7,Fstarted the training, I did a four-
OL,8,Fmile walk on New Year's Day and then
OL,9,Ftwice a week since then I've been out
OL,10,Fwalking.
OL,12,F"I've put the hard work in.
OL,26,@nD@OOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
