OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777114970
OL,3,CVeteran plans to become first triple
OL,4,Camputee to complete London Marathon
OL,6,F"I climbed Kilimanjaro a couple of
OL,7,Fyears ago so I know what kind of
OL,8,Fmental strength these things take when
OL,9,Fit gets a bit tough, where you've got
OL,10,Fto dig in, and I know why I'm doing it
OL,11,F` to hopefully inspire some other
OL,12,Fdisabled people and because some of my
OL,13,Ffriends didn't come home from
OL,14,FAfghanistan unfortunately, so out of
OL,15,Frespect for them.
OL,17,F"I'm still here, so I think it's only
OL,18,Fright to try and do these things and
OL,19,Fremember them guys and girls as well
OL,20,Fwho paid the ultimate sacrifice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
