FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777114971
OL,3,CVeteran plans to become first triple
OL,4,Camputee to complete London Marathon
OL,6,F"I'm still here despite my injury, so
OL,7,FI've got to make the most of life."
OL,9,FThe veteran is hopeful that he will
OL,10,Fcomplete the marathon quicker than
OL,11,Fexpected "with the crowd there and the
OL,12,Fatmosphere", which he said will be an
OL,13,Fimprovement on "walking round and
OL,14,Fround in circles or up and down the
OL,15,Flocal bypass" on his own during his
OL,16,Ftraining.
OL,18,FHis wife will be cheering him on on
OL,19,Fthe day alongside people from the Army
OL,20,FBenevolent Fund (ABF), which helped
OL,21,Fhim after his injury.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]sD@JOUtD@KO]uD@POUwD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
