PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777114971
OL,3,CVeteran plans to become first triple
OL,4,Camputee to complete London Marathon
OL,6,FNear the finish line, the former
OL,7,Fcorporal plans to pay his respects at
OL,8,Fthe Iraq and Afghanistan memorial in
OL,9,FVictoria Gardens.
OL,11,FAsked what emotions he will be feeling
OL,12,Fwhen he finishes, Mr Reid told PA:
OL,13,F"It'll be one of relief, really, I
OL,14,Fthink, and obviously accomplishment.
OL,16,F"I will sit and reflect afterwards
OL,17,Fwhen I get back to the apartment and
OL,18,Fthink wow, that was amazing to be able
OL,19,Fto achieve that."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
