PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777114971
OL,3,CVeteran plans to become first triple
OL,4,Camputee to complete London Marathon
OL,6,FHe will be raising money for the ABF
OL,7,Fand for his own charity ` the Standing
OL,8,FTall Foundation ` which provides
OL,9,Fmental health counselling, addiction,
OL,10,Fhousing and welfare support to
OL,11,Fveterans and communities in his home
OL,12,Ftown.
